node.text: HELLO IG FAM!! Sock is finally contributing to the family with his first sponsorship! And it's with none other than Friskies! specificially Friskies Cat Fishing 2, a game specifically made for cats! Friskies sent over a swag box featuring a cat hoodie, catnip video game controller, an assortment of Friskies products and coupons.. and an IPAD MINI so your cat can play Friskies Cat Fishing 2! To enter, all you need to do is make a video of your cat playing Cat Fishing 2 and tag @Friskies! excited to see all of your entries GOOD LUCK! #friskiespartner #sponsored
